nstructions Development environment setup Feature implementation checklist Testing procedures 7. Risk Assessment Technical risks and mitigation strategies Market risks and competitive analysis Financial risks and contingency planning 8. Resource Requirements Team structure (4-6 people) Cost estimates: $180,000 - $300,000 total Monthly breakdown by development phase 🎯 Key Takeaways for You as a SaaS Founder: It's Absolutely Doable - Modern frameworks make this achievable Start with MVP - Focus on markdown editing + task management first Differentiate Early - Your unique value proposition vs NotePlan/Notion Plan for 9-12 Months - Realistic timeline with proper resources Freemium Model Works - Balance free features with premium value 💰 Revenue Projections: Year 1: $120,000 - $240,000 Year 2: $480,000 - $960,000 Year 3: $1.2M - $2.4M The document is designed specifically for non-developers with: ✅ Clear, tactical SOPs ✅ Step-by-step implementation guides ✅ Visual tables and comparisons ✅ Color-coded sections for easy navigation ✅ Actionable next steps ✅ Resource requirements with expected outcomes Ready to move forward? The document provides everything you need to present to investors, hire a development team, or start building your MVP! NotePlan + Notion Clone Development & Monetization Strategy Click to open Edit in AI Docs Now let me create interactive charts to visualize key aspects of the implementation strategy: Using Tool | MCP Chart Server MCP: generate_column_chart {\"title\":\"Development Phase Timeline & Budget Allocation\",\"axisXTitle\":\"Development Phases\",\"axisYTitle\":\"Time (Weeks) & Budget (K USD)\",\"data\":[{\"category\":\"MVP Core\",\"value\":8,\"group\":\"Timeline (Weeks)\"},{\"category\":\"Rich Editor\",\"value\":6,\"group\":\"Timeline (Weeks)\"},{\"category\":\"Sync & Auth\",\"value\":4,\"group\":\"Timeline (Weeks)\"},{\"category\":\"Mobile App\",\"value\":10,\"group\":\"Timeline (Weeks)\"},{\"category\":\"Advanced Features\",\"value\":12,\"gr